Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:17.75,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:20.74,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.58,0:00:54.69,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,If I can be like the idol, Miki-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.23,0:00:58.50,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,and be just as cool and successful
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:00.85,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,when I
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:03.40,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,start at my new school...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:09.50,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I can make lots...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:10.58,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,and lots...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.44,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,and lots...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:18.27,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,of friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:21.58,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:22.73,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:30.26,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this water's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.26,0:01:32.63,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered who I just saw fall down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:35.81,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Taira-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.81,0:01:37.08,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,Should've known it was you, Komichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:39.61,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.61,0:01:42.21,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,practicing swimming while fully clothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:46.15,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a lift home. Hop in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:51.61,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you got into the middle \Nschool you tested for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:53.55,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Roubai Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:55.60,main,Akebi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a private school!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:59.36,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it's a tough school. \NDidn't your mother go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.36,0:02:03.08,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's why I'm so happy I got in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.08,0:02:04.82,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,Are you, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:08.28,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,They say each class has more \Nthan ten students in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:10.42,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even imagine it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:12.70,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you were always the \Nonly kid in your class
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:14.90,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,back at Futaba Elementary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:16.94,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:19.74,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
