Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:24.19,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,My parents are taking sneak \Nshots of their daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:25.25,main,Yuwa/Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:28.84,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust anyone anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:34.59,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:37.55,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. How was work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:40.46,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.31,0:03:44.23,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe so, but I wasn't \Nsleeping the {\i1}whole{\i0} time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:44.94,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,That's your complaint?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.26,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I was studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:51.75,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better save some cuter \Npictures of me next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:54.96,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:57.21,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought of something...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:58.97,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,but it's a secret for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.04,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:02.64,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:03.91,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to you later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:06.44,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,What'd he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:09.78,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,That he'll do his best at work, \Nso he can be home by next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:12.02,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:16.96,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, ready for the thing \Nyou've been waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:17.57,top,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:18.36,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:25.40,flashback,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I chose Roubai Academy because I've \Nalways wanted to wear a sailor uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:30.74,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I was really nervous at \Nmy exam and interview,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:35.16,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,but now I finally get to wear one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.43,0:04:41.05,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if even someone like \Nme can look good in one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:46.17,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up straight! She can't measure you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:48.32,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:49.42,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:51.42,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,You've gained weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:52.50,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:55.35,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,You did spend a lot of time \Nsitting down to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.68,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,No! No way! I'll drop the weight! I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:05:00.01,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Get changed. It's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:01.09,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Time to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:03.82,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Measure me again later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:09.17,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're going to all the \Ntrouble of making it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:11.16,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let it go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:14.85,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Even in her sleep, all she's been \Ntalking about is sailor uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:15.61,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Kao!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:17.56,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,She was yapping so much, I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:22.22,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, wearing a sailor uniform \Nhas always been your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:24.42,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:27.17,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,So I really have to do a good job on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:31.65,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,What were the kids at Roubai \NAcademy like when you were there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:33.74,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of them were really interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:37.32,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,There were a lot of rich, classy kids, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:39.23,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,The total opposite of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:41.20,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Will I even be able to talk to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:43.20,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,I went in every day thinking, \N"Time to flip the hierarchy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:45.30,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Like I was preparing for war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:52.66,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not as strong as you are, Mom.
