Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:55.20,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Just be who you are, Komichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:58.13,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,All you need is confidence and a smile.
