Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:17.48,sign_8979_128_Chambray,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz4.61\fax-0.08\fsp2\pos(529,24)}Serge/\N\hGabardine {right}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:15.66,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,That was quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:17.49,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,This is a type of fabric called "serge."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:21.22,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make the sailor collar, \Nskirt, and cuffs from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:24.92,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,This is gonna become my sailor suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.23,0:06:29.24,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,And this one is called "gabardine."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:31.45,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use it for the body and sleeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.87,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,There are a few different shades of white.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:35.78,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a matter of preference.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:38.62,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I like the bolder one on the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:42.83,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's so shimmery and smooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:45.52,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't fabric shopping fun, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:46.66,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:49.26,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,I think the ribbon should \Nbe on the larger side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.13,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,It'll look cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.02,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:52.76,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, do you need help?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.81,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:56.99,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,It's the stripes that make a sailor uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:06:58.54,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.04,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! I like this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:07.65,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,You've been humming all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:08.55,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:12.08,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice that you're happy, \Nbut think about how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:14.31,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:17.84,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You had to be patient and wait \Nthe whole time I was studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:18.82,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:23.98,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to go to \Nschool with me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:25.43,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that make you sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:35.33,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you were \Nexcited to go by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:36.82,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:38.29,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You did, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:43.74,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it makes me kinda sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:51.16,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be in third grade, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:54.20,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll be in your first year again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.95,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:08:00.69,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You know what? I'm just \Nas nervous as I am happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:03.42,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I'll be \Nable to make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:06.46,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of kids from Tokyo go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:10.20,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help wondering if \NI'll be able to keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.22,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:16.23,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause you're really cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:18.30,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:21.26,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You don't even believe me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:23.27,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:28.18,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:32.33,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,We'll both be on our own. Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:33.27,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.35,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Komichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:40.55,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:43.29,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:44.55,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:46.28,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,This is known as "tacking."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:49.50,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,We use a different fabric to get all the \Ndetails set before making the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:52.74,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know making a \Nuniform was so much work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.30,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:05.60,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,The laundry's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:07.80,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do the cleaning, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:11.13,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:14.35,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I'll do the dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:16.35,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I'm almost done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:18.36,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:23.80,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, you're wasting water!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:36.94,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Komichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:38.81,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Come on over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:52.51,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:54.38,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:57.88,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Here, try it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:03.55,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:07.96,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:24.33,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:26.00,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you're a little too young for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:27.54,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.66,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, you look so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:42.47,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Komichi, does it fit okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:44.65,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:49.46,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:53.85,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:01.99,sign_17263_208_Roubai_Academy_M,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(125,20)}Roubai Academy Middle School \N{\fs15}Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:05.70,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,A few things have changed, \Nbut it really brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.25,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:12.93,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's a new student... Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:15.07,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:17.59,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Blazers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:19.08,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Komichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:22.32,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Is there some other event going on today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:24.18,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:29.34,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to congratulate you all on \Nyour acceptance into this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:33.64,main,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,As of today, you are all \Nstudents of Roubai Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.35,italics,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Komichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:38.35,top,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,For many years, this school has prepared \Nmany excellent students for...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:38.16,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:43.92,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:45.82,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:48.71,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, how'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:50.30,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:53.32,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:57.14,flashback,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry I didn't confirm \Nwhat the uniform was first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:13:00.30,flashback,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the students did wear sailor \Nuniforms when you attended here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:01.64,flashback,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:08.40,flashback,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we've known since the interview that \NKomichi-san dreamed of wearing a sailor uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:12.81,flashback,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,It's our fault for not \Ninforming her at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:17.87,flashback,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,I understand Yuwa-san made it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:21.85,flashback,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! We picked out the \Nfabrics together, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:23.86,flashback,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:27.31,flashback,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,My mother made my school uniform, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.31,0:13:29.83,flashback,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,It made me so very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:33.45,flashback,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,Considering the circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:37.90,flashback,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,the school will permit Komichi-san \Nto wear her sailor uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.24,flashback,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,Principal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:42.95,flashback,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,It is an accepted uniform of this school,\N albeit one from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:45.10,flashback,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,We have no reason to forbid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:51.02,flashback,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,But I will leave the final decision \Nto Komichi-san and her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:56.86,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll only be me. That's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:00.27,sign_20093_244_Middle_School_En,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0F3A5F&\3c&H407EA8&}Middle School Entrance Exams 76:  {\3c&H16217D&\c&H001032&}Roubai Academy Middle School\N{\b0\fnVerdana\c&H0E3155&\3c&H356B98&} Science: {\c&H0C2B3E&}Memorization Check\N{\fnTrebuchet MS\c&H0A2441&\3c&H3277A0&} Getting Along Well With Other People\N{\b1\c&H132C71&\3c&H4D6B7F&}Sewing {\c&H0B2A3D&}for Beginners\N {\fnArial\c&H4D748F&\3c&H253400&}Marine Field Guide: Creatures of the Sea\N{\fnVerdana\b0\c&H001A41&\3c&H073B7F&} Reptiles and Amphibians of Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:09.76,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Your congratulatory dinner is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:12.60,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,You get two egg yolks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:15.25,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Kao, did you hear what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.10,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:19.06,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Blazers are cute too, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:25.06,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:26.85,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:31.21,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,So now you hate the sailor \Nuniform Mom made for you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:33.41,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:36.32,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,You're not cool anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:37.93,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:46.73,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:52.53,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hate it. I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:56.07,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want everyone \Nto think I'm weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:59.07,flashback,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause you're really cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:04.09,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be seen as cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:08.52,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,And I want to make lots of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:13.59,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm the only one in a sailor uniform,\N I know I'll stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:16.07,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that'll be my chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:37.78,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:39.61,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:52.28,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:55.80,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Komichi... Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:59.66,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Confidence and a smile, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:02.88,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Go get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:06.07,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Off I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:20.66,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:23.65,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... I cut it kinda close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:39.96,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:40.67,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:43.36,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've sobered up a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:46.59,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:48.18,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:55.85,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry blossoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:17.76,sign_24797_279_Roubai_Academy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fay.2\move(475,275,475,-18)}Roubai\N\hAcademy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:23.98,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I think... I got... a little too fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:30.59,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's so big! It looks like a castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.46,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Am I the first one here?
