Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:47.71,top,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I've got seat number 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:49.29,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Class 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:57.99,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:02.42,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's already here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:05.84,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,What if she's really scary?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:08.35,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what a weird outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:10.84,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:13.74,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,We should try to get along!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:14.49,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Osu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:18.53,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I trying to fight them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:46.77,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:49.05,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:52.54,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Good... morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:58.33,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Please forget you ever saw that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:18:59.32,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:03.02,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... you saw me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:06.03,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,When I was smelling my own \Nfeet on the nail clippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:08.40,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's what she was doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:10.83,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:13.81,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,But... do your feet smell that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:15.33,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't question me about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.33,0:19:17.07,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm embarrassed enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:18.83,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm curious now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:21.84,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:25.85,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I ran here, so I think they \Nmight smell a little sweaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:28.81,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I can see how you'd get into it, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:33.52,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,You're kind of interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:35.89,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I did it, Kao!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:38.57,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,She called your sister "interesting"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:42.86,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Would you mind talking \Nwith me a little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:50.69,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... So you're going to wear \Nthe sailor uniform from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.69,0:19:52.21,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty gutsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:57.12,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You're Kizaki Erika-san, \Nand you're from T-Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:58.48,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:00.14,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:02.12,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,You're very diligent, Akebi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.17,0:20:08.90,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your nail clippers are really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.65,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you carry them around all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:12.64,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:16.14,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,In my room at home, \Nwhen I get anxious or nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:18.65,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,I end up clipping my nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:23.15,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,This clicking sound just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:25.15,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,relaxes me somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:31.29,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Were you anxious just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:31.97,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:37.92,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Well... with all the firsts \NI'm experiencing today,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:39.65,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't sleep last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:43.74,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,I came to school early because \NI couldn't just sit around any longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:45.52,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,but I just kept getting more nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:53.19,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:55.75,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:59.85,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I was just surprised someone as pretty \Nas you would stress like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:01.64,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:03.69,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,And my looks have nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:05.69,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:08.34,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I was kinda scared, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:11.47,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I've never really talked to \Nsomeone my own age before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:16.19,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what I'd do if I didn't \Nthink the way everyone else does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:18.28,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:19.70,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I felt the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.81,0:21:25.67,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess everyone else \Nwill be coming in soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.67,0:21:28.52,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,I was just sitting at a random desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.21,0:21:31.43,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Number 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:33.39,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,This one's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:37.57,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,The closest spot to greet \Neveryone coming in...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:39.07,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm number 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:51.78,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've calmed down a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:56.86,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:04.04,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can do this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:08.09,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
